

Increment / Decrement Operator (++, --) : It'll increment or decrement the value of variable by 1

++ : increment the value of variable by 1
-- : decrement the value of variable by 1

Postfix Operator

exp++;
* operator comes after the variable
* first complete all other operations and then increment the value of variable

Prefix Operator

++exp;
* operator comes before the variable
* first increment the value of variable and then complete all other operations
